tps://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A3-B%E1%BA%A3n-Trung/author--bPkY2P4ts3ashmJU5RNJQ">Lã Bản Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Nam-Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung/poem-BMkQRdDALat1QVkZh01GPg">Nam Quan đạo trung - 南關道中</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BA%BF-hu%E1%BB%81/poem-JXohIo6JeLgcmlkUtOITzQ">Phế huề - 廢畦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Thu-song-phong-v%C5%A9-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-nK0tnLa3M6iVye_Tji5Umg">Thu song phong vũ tịch - 秋窗風雨夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/T%E1%BB%B1-qu%C3%A2n-chi-xu%E1%BA%A5t-h%C4%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-gE83OKZ9TkSegJI2EHdeUQ">Tự quân chi xuất hĩ kỳ 3 - 自君之出矣其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/author-xRXhuUOmluK39LpCU7hkCA">Trương Cửu Linh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
